calc.model

Class RevPolishCalc

  • java.lang.Object
    • calc.model.RevPolishCalc
  • All Implemented Interfaces:
    CalcInterface

    public class RevPolishCalc
extends java.lang.Object
implements CalcInterface
    The RevPolishCalc class is used to evaluate postfix expression strings, by implementing the Visitor design pattern to traverse a binary tree of the expression, and calculate the answer.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
